## Quality Checks

### Read Statistics Interpretation

| Metric | RS II (Typical) | Sequel II (Typical) | Indication |
|--------|-----------------|-------------------|-----------|
| **Reads per File** | 50k - 100k | 500k - 1M | Normal range |
| **Spots = Reads Written** | 1:1 ratio | 1:1 ratio | ✅ Data integrity OK |
| **Adapter Detection** | <5% | <5% | Acceptable quality |

> ✅ **Expected Sign**: 1:1 ratio between spots read, reads read, and reads written indicates clean data transfer.

